.TH ZOOMIX 1 "June 2026" "zoomix 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
zoomix \- screen zoom, annotation, and image snip utility for Linux Mint X11
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zoomix
.SH DESCRIPTION
Zoomix provides ZoomIt-style zooming, on-screen drawing/text annotation, and image snip capture on Linux Mint Cinnamon X11 sessions.
.SH DEFAULT HOTKEYS
.TP
.B Ctrl+1
Open zoom mode.
.TP
.B Ctrl+4
Open live zoom mode.
.TP
.B Ctrl+2
Open draw mode.
.TP
.B Ctrl+3
Open snip mode.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/zoomix/config.toml
User configuration file.
.TP
.I ~/Pictures/Zoomix
Default screenshot output directory.
.SH LIMITATIONS
This version targets X11. Wayland, video capture, timer, DemoType, and OCR behavior are not implemented.
